Title: The Right Food...
Description:
<The plant is now a promising sapling and has thrived with the attention you've given.

Peering closely at the plant's leaves, you see its exterior brimming with dew. Perhaps the right food will help the plant even further.>
ObjectivesText: Bring some fertilizer for the plant.

Objectives.Text: Combine the Fertilizer Compound using the Plant Matter
Wait for the Fertilizer to finish composting
Spread the completed fertilizer around the sapling
Entertain the plant with a few words
Acquire Five Plant Matter from Verdant Emerald Lashers
